4
00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:26.580
population.

5
00:00:27.140 --> 00:00:33.500
2.500 years later. in Sri Lanka. the city of Anura Dapura had a similar problem.

6
00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:41.220
They were also growing constantly. and like Uruk. their city relied heavily on an elaborate irrigation system.

7
00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:47.740
As Uruk grew. its farmers began chopping down trees to make space for more crops.

8
00:00:48.380 --> 00:00:51.320
In Anura Dapura. however. trees were sacred.

9
00:00:51.320 --> 00:00:57.440
Their city housed an offshoot of the Bodhi tree. under which Buddha himself was said to have

10
