mineral deposits. which rendered the soil too salty for agriculture. Conversely.

14
00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:29.620
Anura Dapura's irrigation system was designed to work in concert with the surrounding forest.

15
00:01:30.180 --> 00:01:34.700
Their city eventually grew to more than twice Uruk's population. and today.

16
00:01:35.160 --> 00:01:39.800
Anura Dapura still cares for a tree planted over 2.000 years ago.

17
