runoff before releasing it back into the atmosphere. The webs of their roots protect against mudslides.

20
00:01:59.660 --> 00:02:05.320
while allowing soil to retain water and filter out toxins. Roots help prevent floods.

21
00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:11.440
while reducing the need for storm drains and water treatment plants. Their porous leaves purify

22
